column5: Started the Jeep a few minutes ago to come home from grabbing a few groceries and it started to beep every 10 secs and flashed a warning  " LOWASH "  I immediately assume it is LOW ASH and something to do with the emissions, Thankyou google for clearing up that only the windshield washer fluid is low
lol I thought the same thing first time i saw that on my jeep diesel

lol I thought the same thing first time i saw that on my jeep diesel  Terry , I remember I picked up my silver 2006 Liberty and don't you post an identical vehicle a few days later, exactly same trim and colour but a CRD. 10 years old and 75,000 km.,I need to get out more
Low ash! That's terrible - better add more coal to your fuel mixture ?
